Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.29,0:02:02.29,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Stratili sme zvuk lodnej skrutky malej ponorky z Odysea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:07.00,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Nech flotila prehľadáva oblasť, kde zmizla.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:21.89,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Motory vpred, pomalý chod!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:45.79,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Si to ty, Joze?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.79,0:02:48.29,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno! Hlásim príchod.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:51.30,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže si sa vrátila.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.46,0:02:53.17,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobrá práca.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:02:56.68,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:02:58.80,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Vstúpte a pripravte sa na odchod!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:25.33,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ach, to je Majuge!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.54,0:03:27.67,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs10}Majuge  = obočie
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.75,0:03:27.67,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Majuge? Tak sa volá?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.92,0:03:29.67,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to dobré meno.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:31.46,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:33.05,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Si v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:37.68,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako sa máš?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:42.72,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Au! To bolí!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:46.06,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáčte!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:50.86,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Keel...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:19.26,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcem videť tú mapu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:23.89,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Tú, ktorú vyrobil otec.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.56,0:04:27.89,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja som mu o nej povedal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:35.23,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre teda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.83,0:04:49.16,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Pripraviť SM-3!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:51.17,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Záchytné strely?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:55.71,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Donútil tie deti hľadať útočisko na tejto lodi. Je toho schopný.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:04:57.67,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Pripravte SM-3.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:13.44,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Musíte sa porozprávať o dôležitých veciach, my zatiaľ pôjdeme.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:16.36,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Isla!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:18.44,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcem, aby sme ju videli spolu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:20.45,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:41.38,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,To je nádhera!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.77,0:05:54.31,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Otec tam zostal kvôli tomuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:55.19,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.36,0:05:57.19,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie je to zlé!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:00.44,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, Aoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:01.40,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.03,0:06:04.66,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcem túto mapu oznámiť všetkým.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:10.83,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Chceme otcovu mapu oznámiť celému svetu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:13.17,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Oznámiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:16.71,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Presne tak! Chceme ju ukázať všetkým!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.25,0:06:21.92,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Váš otec je naozaj obdivuhodný muž.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.72,0:06:29.68,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Bez tejto mapy by sme sa ťažko spamätávali po Kladive Edenu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:36.06,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Preto nedovolím, aby sa táto mapa stala zárodkom konfliktov!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:40.28,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak sa o mape dozvie verejnosť, ľudia ju budú chcieť využiť vo svoj prospech.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.82,0:06:42.82,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Svet znova zachváti vojna.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.49,0:06:45.82,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanešťastie, toho sa obávam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:49.33,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale veď už predsa je... vojna.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:52.16,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,S Gouldom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.12,0:06:54.08,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Je vojna!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.96,0:06:56.63,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Kapitán!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.21,0:06:59.50,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Odyseus otvára SLBM poklopy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.97,0:07:11.47,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Pripravte Falangu na rýchlu paľbu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:17.90,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Kapitán Gould tiež chce navždy ukončiť nepokoje!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:22.19,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj keď sa vaše metódy líšia,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:24.24,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,nie je váš cieľ spoločný?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:27.28,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Spamätať sa z Kladiva Edenu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.20,0:07:30.74,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Vytvoriť nový svet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.33,0:07:31.91,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:35.00,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo musela vypuknúť vojna?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:40.09,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Preto trvám na tom, aby aj náš ostrov mal právo veta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:45.01,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Náš ostrov produkuje štvrtinu svetových zásob jedla!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:49.30,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Preto by sme mali ukázať mapu všetkým!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:58.06,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak mapu zverejníme, potom budú všetci\Nna svete na rovnakej štartovacej čiare.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:00.02,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Práve teraz...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.02,0:08:02.40,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,...máme šancu vybudovať nový svet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:03.61,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ľudia...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:07.45,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,S ľuďmi to nie je také jednoduché.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:09.87,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo im neveríš?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:16.04,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Odkedy som opustil Yabitsu, stretol som len samých dobrých ľudí!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:22.04,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja im verím! Chcem im ukázať mapu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:27.42,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Možno všetkému nerozumiem...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:30.55,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,...ale nie je trocha podozrivé, že si nechávaš mapu pre seba, Aoi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.10,0:08:37.85,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Náš otec veril, že táto mapa pomôže vybudovať nový svet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:39.94,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Preto zostal vo vesmíre, sám.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:44.98,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Dovoľte prosím, aby táto mapa pomohla svetu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:48.15,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to mapa nášho otca.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.45,0:08:50.20,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,To je...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:53.00,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Odyseus otvoril SLBM poklopy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:55.95,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Teen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.42,0:09:03.29,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Zaplavte komory!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:04.21,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Rýchlo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.55,0:09:05.00,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Rýchlo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.52,0:09:24.11,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Kapitán!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.33,0:09:39.08,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Zostaň tu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:50.84,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Pripraviť na boj!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:52.55,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Spustiť radiačné štíty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:09:59.60,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Gould!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:04.23,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím, pusťte ma dnu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:08.36,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím vás!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.11,0:10:11.15,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,MAD: Odyseus zameraný!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:12.91,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,ASROCK: protiponorkové rakety pripravené!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:14.99,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Generálna sekretárka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:18.37,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Gould vlastní jadrové zbrane.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:20.75,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Má v pláne vypáliť SLBM.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.54,0:10:24.46,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Chce zničiť svet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:27.75,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Kapitán Satojama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:32.80,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Gould už nie je ten Gould, akého sme poznali!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:34.89,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Musíme ho potopiť!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.51,0:10:41.18,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Kapitán! To by ste nikdy neurobili.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.81,0:10:43.06,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Nešli by ste tak ďaleko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:45.56,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Vy, ktorý zo všetko najviac nenávidíte boj!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.31,0:10:49.15,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Zničiť svet... tomu neverím!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.03,0:10:54.82,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,To bol Teen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.24,0:10:56.91,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Pobočník? Čo hovorí?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:59.03,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Že by sme mali vyplávať na povrch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:10:59.83,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Na povrch?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.83,0:11:03.33,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže sa vybral vlastnou cestou...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:06.54,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:09.34,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Blíži sa všeobecný útok!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:11.96,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetky ASROCK-y, páľ!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.30,0:11:12.97,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Počkajte!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:16.18,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Dajte nám ešte jednu šancu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:18.05,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Žiadna šanca už nie je.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.85,0:11:19.85,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Vypáľte ich jednu po druhej!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:26.77,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Spojte sa so Sandžunom v NORAD-e.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:31.65,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Povedzte mu, nech informuje všetky krajiny v dosahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.69,0:11:34.53,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Nech varuje celý svet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.03,0:11:35.53,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozkaz!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:39.83,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Kapitán...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:44.16,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,SLBM...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:03.89,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Kapitán!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:14.57,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Deväť torpéd za nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.11,0:12:15.94,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Dve z druhej strany!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.45,0:12:18.32,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Dve záchytné siete zozadu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:21.91,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepnite na druhú skrutku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.30,0:12:37.34,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Torpéda vpredu zmenili kurz.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:39.01,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobrá práca, Satojama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:42.10,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Neskočíš dvakrát na ten istý trik.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.77,0:12:46.23,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Joze!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.60,0:12:47.14,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:49.60,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,To je kľúč od spúšťača.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.27,0:12:52.11,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, ukončím to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:07.87,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Odyseus?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.96,0:13:09.96,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Stále je tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.96,0:13:13.63,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz vypáli SLBM!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:21.97,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,H-hej, Teen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:35.27,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Stoj, ty idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:37.82,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to nebezpečné!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.44,0:13:39.49,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Pusť!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.16,0:13:45.28,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Páľ!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:55.09,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,To bolí!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.84,0:13:57.00,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak nezastavím kapitána...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:00.22,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.26,0:14:07.10,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Blížia sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.10,0:14:09.39,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Falanga! Rýchla paľba!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:33.71,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Kapitán...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.67,0:14:38.92,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,To nemôže byť pravda!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.03,0:15:07.74,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Jedna zostrelená...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:09.08,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,A čo zvyšné dve?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:11.50,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Smerujú ku Gi a Amerike.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:17.29,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Urýchlene pošlite varovnú správu Gi a Amerike.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.29,0:15:17.84,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozkaz!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:19.25,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Pre tých, čo prežijú...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.84,0:15:26.55,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Zorganizujte záchranný tím pre preživších.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:26.84,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, madam!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.27,0:15:34.77,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Kapitán!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.27,0:15:36.94,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Stratili sme Odysea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.52,0:15:38.06,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Stratili?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:08.26,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem vám.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.44,0:16:22.77,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Kontaktujte Blatyrea a NORAD.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:25.61,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Zistite veľkosť škôd.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:26.24,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Kapitán!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.07,0:16:28.28,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Máme správu z Gi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:29.53,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Čože?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.19,0:16:59.98,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurá!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.44,0:17:01.06,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:04.48,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa stalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:06.94,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Keel, sú v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:08.78,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevybuchli.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:11.20,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to znamená?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:16.91,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Nukleárne hlavice bômb, ktoré zasiahli Gi a Ameriku, nevybuchli.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.37,0:17:20.04,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Práve sme dostali správy z oboch krajín.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:21.04,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevybuchnuté bomby?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:27.55,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Odyseove SLBM boli vyrobené ešte pred Kladivom Edenu. Boli dosť staré.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:31.09,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevybuchli, pretože boli po záruke?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.18,0:17:33.30,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to má znamenať?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.89,0:17:35.06,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže ani jedna?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:38.02,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, neboli žiadne škody.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.02,0:17:39.10,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Vďakabohu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:40.77,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Vďakabohu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.44,0:17:47.69,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Unmao, starká a všetci! Sú v poriadku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.03,0:17:51.07,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako poznám Goulda, nestalo sa to kvôli zlej údržbe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.86,0:17:55.20,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Dočerta! Použil SLBM, aby mohol zatiaľ ujsť?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.41,0:17:57.04,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Kapitán...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:04.59,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakoniec nebude doba, v ktorej nebudú existovať vojny.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:08.71,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Niekto vždy využije vojenskú silu, aby zvíťazil nad svojimi protivníkmi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:11.55,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Keď smútok a nenávisť skončia,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:13.93,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,príde ďalšia vojna.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.55,0:18:15.60,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to večný kolobeh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:18.10,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale ja tomu verím.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:21.73,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Verím, že raz príde deň, keď nebudú vojny a všetci budú žiť v mieri.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.73,0:18:25.11,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Verím v ľudstvo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.99,0:18:33.61,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoi, vybudujeme ten nový svet spolu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.41,0:18:38.70,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Svet bez vojny? Nový svet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:41.16,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Sľúb mi to, Aoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:44.37,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Že vybudujeme nový svet spoločne.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:50.96,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,To bolo pred Kladivom Edenu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.92,0:18:57.01,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Verila som tomu. A aj keď som tomu stále verila...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.56,0:19:03.89,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,...neviem, kedy som prestala veriť v ľudí.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:11.23,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Volá sa Keel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:13.40,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Keel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:17.16,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie! Nie je to Keelovo dieťa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.87,0:19:18.16,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ach...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.33,0:19:19.91,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Keel...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.33,0:19:26.29,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Teda veľký Keel sa vydal vlastnou cestou.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.63,0:19:34.26,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Keel by povedal, že Aoi je klamárka a hnusná stará ježibaba, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.51,0:19:36.47,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,To by naozaj povedal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:41.60,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,No... teda... chcem tým povedať...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:44.64,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Keel bude v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.60,0:19:47.52,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Asi máš pravdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.98,0:19:52.53,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,On... obaja budú v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:20:00.83,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevedel som, že Zem je naozaj modrá.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:03.50,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Nehovoril nám to otec stále?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:07.75,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Že na Zemi sú modré moria a zelené hory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.21,0:20:10.84,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,A červené a žlté... kvety všetkých farieb.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.88,0:20:14.34,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, vesmír je úplne čierny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.13,0:20:17.80,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Som rád,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:18.55,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,že sme prišli na Zem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.05,0:20:21.01,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Asi hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.36,0:20:34.65,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Zverujem vám túto mapu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.11,0:20:36.57,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Generálna sekretárka, to je...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.24,0:20:40.12,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:43.41,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj ja verím v tú cestu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:21:00.09,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ktovie, na čo sa teraz otec pozerá...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.64,0:21:03.60,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Určite na Zem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.39,0:21:05.22,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Asi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:11.06,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ktovie, na čo sa teraz pozerajú.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.12,0:21:23.12,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Obloha je taká modrá!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.91,0:21:25.37,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, modrá.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.83,0:21:27.75,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Keel! Teen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.33,0:21:30.21,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Raňajky sú na stole!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:33.13,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Vďaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:35.80,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Kto bude prvý, vyhráva nášup!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.59,0:21:40.88,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja si beriem omeletu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.18,0:21:41.97,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Nepredbehneš ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.68,0:21:58.77,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Koremade umaku yareta ka\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Robil som to doteraz správne?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.85,0:22:00.54,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Korekara dosureba ii ka\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Čo mám teraz robiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.62,0:22:05.42,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonna koto kangaeta koto nante nai\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Nikdy som o tom nepremýšľal
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.49,0:22:07.39,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Omoi mo yoranai koudo\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Spontánne rozhodnutia
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.66,0:22:11.79,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yosou mo tsukanai jyokyo kamawanai\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Nečakané situácie, to som ja
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.29,0:22:14.19,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorekoso sonzai shomei\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}To je môj život
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.30,0:22:15.42,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,YES, I’M DOING NOW\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Áno, som to ja
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.53,0:22:18.47,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Tesagurinagara mo mada minu sekai wo sozo chu\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Mám svet vo svojich rukách, aj keď som ho nevidel
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.70,0:22:19.32,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,CHECK NOW\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Tak sleduj
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:22.10,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotae ga hitotsudakenaraba kase o tori harau\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Ak jediná možnosť je pretrhnúť okovy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.17,0:22:23.26,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,ANSWER 2\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Urob to
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.34,0:22:24.80,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,LIMIT OFF, READY TO ROLL\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Hranice padajú, priprav sa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.87,0:22:25.40,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,FOCUS\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Sústreď sa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:26.84,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoten awase suguni\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Náš cieľ je spoločný
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.91,0:22:27.27,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,GET ON\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Nasadaj
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.34,0:22:31.78,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Norikoete ikeruhazu tafu kiwamari nai hibi mo\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Vznesieme sa nad ťažké nekonečné dni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:35.71,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Doshitemo tsutaetainda\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Chcem ti len povedať
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.15,0:22:38.02,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,OK OK\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Je to OK, OK
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.15,0:22:40.88,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotoba ni kaete iko\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Poviem to slovami
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.96,0:22:44.69,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsudatte kono mune ni\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Budeš navždy v mojom srdci
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.79,0:22:46.92,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,OH YEAH OH YEAH\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Áno, áno
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.03,0:22:50.02,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yadoru omoi tachi o\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Na tom sa nič nezmení
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.10,0:22:52.07,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Sekaiju ni hirogaru youni\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Poviem to slovami, poviem to všetkým
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.13,0:22:54.12,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotoba ni kaete tsutaete iko\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Nech to vie celý svet
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.20,0:22:56.17,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuyoku omou imadakara koso\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Verím, že teraz je ten čas
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.24,0:22:58.67,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotoba ni kaete tsutaete iko\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Povedať to slovami, povedať to všetkým
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.31,0:23:02.57,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuyoku nari hibiku koe\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Silným hlasom, čo sa nesie do diaľky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.68,0:23:07.91,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Karenai inori to tomoni\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}A modlitbou, čo nikdy neumrie
